### Tarea 7 — REST API Test File
### Use with REST Client extension in VSCode

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### GET all products (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos

###

### GET with pagination and sorting
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos?page=1&limit=20&sort=id_asc

###

### GET sorted by price ascending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos?page=1&limit=10&sort=precio_asc

###

### GET sorted by price descending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos?page=1&limit=10&sort=precio_desc

###

### GET with text search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos?search=lámina

###

### GET with price filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos?minPrice=10&maxPrice=50

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### GET product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos/1

###

### GET product that doesn't exist (returns 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/productos/9999

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### POST — create new product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/productos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "título": "Lámina de prueba",
  "descripción": "Una descripción de prueba para el producto de test",
  "precio": 25.50,
  "imagen": "lamina_prueba.jpg"
}

###

### POST — missing fields (returns 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/productos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "título": "Sin descripción"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### PUT — update product (change id as needed)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/productos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "título": "Título actualizado desde REST Client",
  "descripción": "Descripción actualizada correctamente",
  "precio": 35.99
}

###

### PUT — product not found (returns 404)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/productos/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "título": "No existe"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────
### DELETE — delete product (change id as needed)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/productos/20

###

### DELETE — product not found (returns 404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/productos/9999

###
